Syntax: mmon
This command allows you to enable and disable your monk monitor.

The monk monitor now shows:
  style
  current chi and max chi
  whether chi focus is active
  the current power word, if any
  your combo summary
  the active trial objective, if you are in a mastery trial

The two bracket indicators are:
  first bracket: chi focus
  second bracket: power word

Examples:
  [F] means chi focus is active
  [X] means it is not
  [S] [C] [D] [A] indicate the active power word
